---
const base = '/ApuntesWeb/';
---

<html lang="es">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
		<title>404 | Apuntes Ingeniería Informática</title>
		<style>
			:root {
				color-scheme: light dark;
				font-family: "Public Sans", system-ui, sans-serif;
			}

			body {
				margin: 0;
				min-height: 100vh;
				display: grid;
				place-items: center;
				background:
					radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(180, 93, 39, 0.18), transparent 32%),
					linear-gradient(180deg, #f7f2e9, #ece3d4);
				color: #281f18;
			}

			main {
				width: min(640px, calc(100% - 3rem));
				padding: 3rem;
				border: 1px solid rgba(86, 71, 55, 0.14);
				background: rgba(255, 252, 245, 0.88);
				box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(63, 41, 24, 0.12);
				backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
			}

			h1 {
				margin: 0 0 1rem;
				font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 5rem);
				line-height: 0.95;
				font-family: "Fraunces", Georgia, serif;
			}

			p {
				margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
				font-size: 1.05rem;
				line-height: 1.6;
			}

			a {
				color: #6f2f11;
				font-weight: 700;
			}
		</style>
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
		<link
			href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:opsz,wght@9..144,700&family=Public+Sans:wght@400;600;700&display=swap"
			rel="stylesheet"
		/>
	</head>
	<body>
		<main>
			<h1>404</h1>
			<p>La página que buscas no existe o ha cambiado de ruta.</p>
			<p><a href={base}>Volver al inicio</a></p>
		</main>
	</body>
</html>
